### ===========================================
### Calculator SOAP Service — HTTP Tests
###
### SOAP Requests werden als POST mit XML Body gesendet.
### Voraussetzung: WildFly läuft mit cdi-demo deployed.
### ===========================================

@host = http://localhost:8080
@app = soap-demo

### WSDL abrufen (im Browser oder hier)
GET {{host}}/{{app}}/CalculatorService?wsdl
Accept: text/xml

### Addition: 10 + 20
POST {{host}}/{{app}}/CalculatorService
Content-Type: text/xml

<soap:Envelope xmlns:soap="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/"
               xmlns:calc="http://soap.training.cgsit.com/">
    <soap:Body>
        <calc:add>
            <a>10</a>
            <b>20</b>
        </calc:add>
    </soap:Body>
</soap:Envelope>

### Multiplikation: 6 × 7
POST {{host}}/{{app}}/CalculatorService
Content-Type: text/xml

<soap:Envelope xmlns:soap="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/"
               xmlns:calc="http://soap.training.cgsit.com/">
    <soap:Body>
        <calc:multiply>
            <a>6</a>
            <b>7</b>
        </calc:multiply>
    </soap:Body>
</soap:Envelope>

### Division: 100 / 3
POST {{host}}/{{app}}/CalculatorService
Content-Type: text/xml

<soap:Envelope xmlns:soap="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/"
               xmlns:calc="http://soap.training.cgsit.com/">
    <soap:Body>
        <calc:divide>
            <a>100</a>
            <b>3</b>
        </calc:divide>
    </soap:Body>
</soap:Envelope>

### Division durch 0 — Fehler
POST {{host}}/{{app}}/CalculatorService
Content-Type: text/xml

<soap:Envelope xmlns:soap="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/"
               xmlns:calc="http://soap.training.cgsit.com/">
    <soap:Body>
        <calc:divide>
            <a>42</a>
            <b>0</b>
        </calc:divide>
    </soap:Body>
</soap:Envelope>
